d":"ac3f3dc2471f73fc37c498b53fea094d4f6a8c9a","tid":423360,"uid":80624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加泰羅尼亞人退出晒西班牙隊，應該都唔會影響到西班牙既實力</blockquote><br />\n肯定差幾班喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n數黎聽聽</blockquote><br />\n幾年前就係<br />\n而家加泰人係西班牙隊都無乜剩幾多個打到主力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}